{"tid":1171431,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個細個講過嘅仆街嘢","createTime":"2019-05-25T16:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T17:42:15.000Z","uid":224234,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"63e3453b82635ea5244a4549b8ba34f18fc1452c","tid":1171431,"uid":224234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T16:52:14.000Z","msg":"話說小一二嗰陣拖住老母行街， 咁啱見到有幾個工人打開渠蓋做嘢， 我專登大大聲講:「 咁臭嘅，啲人好污糟」 <br />\n<br />\n之後當然畀人屌到上天，老母叫我講對唔住，我就同個工人話:「 媽咪叫你講對唔住， 因為講粗口係唔啱㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n老母應該驚我畀人掉落坑渠即刻拉住我走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真心想同佢哋講對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2981c82a819b7c972e41da476bc3c93de42e3319","tid":1171431,"uid":201061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T16:56:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"816c5b1b92897fe108cb9a1f81a01ad5b6c9985f","tid":1171431,"uid":280,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T17:07:17.000Z","msg":"係街到同老豆講 我唔係你生嫁 你唔係我家人<br />\n之後俾佢一個Side kick 踢左我埋牆"},{"pid":"1ee328d330e2849f29a9dc76165697e53312cb9d","tid":1171431,"uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T17:12:22.000Z","msg":"覺得福字米粉好臭 跟住話好大陣公廁味<br />\n<br />\n喺街見到一啲身體殘障或弱智人士<br />\n會唔停望住人"},{"pid":"66706ffa2db4be6a1eceee8272f9c0167fe53ca3","tid":1171431,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T17:17:20.000Z","msg":"同個女仔講：你唔好掂我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"778362534c87e01bdc40fc80f8be68feb7a5b345","tid":1171431,"uid":224234,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"66706ffa2db4be6a1eceee8272f9c0167fe53